item.description:
How Michigan is looking for-and creating-opportunities for economic growth

Michiganders and their businesses touch many fields. From technology and renewable energy, to aviation and aeronautics, the food and beverage industry, and, of course, automotive, there is a great deal going on. Often these Michigan businesses are leaders in their respective sectors. The importance of this economic landscape lies in Michigan's diversity.
